section.div: This repository will assist you in creating a more beautiful and appealing github profile, and you will have access to a comprehensive range of tools and tutorials for beautifying your github profile.
Add dynamically generated GitHub Stat Trophies on your readme
OpenAI ChatGPT, Whisper, GPT-3 , GPT-4, Azure OpenAI and DALL-E dotnet SDK
An infographics generator with 30+ plugins and 300+ options to display stats about your GitHub account and render them as SVG, Markdown, PDF or JSON!

div.div: v0.1.7 - Pt. 1 Added Stamina Regen Reworked some Attack and Weapon constructors Item overviews can now use the creature and item holder Agility now gives +1 DT every other level Session removal works now Players counts are accurate now Added 30 message cap for client logs Location creature lists are now unique lists (HashSets) - Might fix the multiple copies of player glitch? Increased floor sizes (min: 5 -> 10, max: 15 -> 17) You can no longer use attacks you don't have the stamina for Sell menu now factors in sell cut in the final message Grave Robbing++ (take all button) Added 30% stamina regen multiplier while weight carried exceeds max weight Wisdom now gives +2% xp (rounded up) Level before player names now has styling based on the level +Pt. 2 content coming later today!
Fixed out of memory issue with logs
Added player count to bot status
